3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-6a3c8dbb7c9ef\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-nang-khieu\/#GIA_SU_NANG_KHIEU\" >GIA S\u01af N\u0102NG KHI\u1ebeU<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-nang-khieu\/#1Nhung_kho_khan_cua_hoc_sinh_khi_hoc_Toan\" >1.Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh khi h\u1ecdc To\u00e1n?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-nang-khieu\/#2Trung_tam_gia_su_Tri_Viet_%E2%80%93_dia_chi_uy_tin_so_1_Ha_Noi\" >2.Trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh \u2013 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 uy t\u00edn s\u1ed1 1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-nang-khieu\/#3Bang_gia_gia_su_chuyen_Toan\" >3.B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-nang-khieu\/#4Doi_ngu_gia_su_chuyen_Toan\" >4.\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-5' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-5'><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-5' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-5'><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-5' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-5'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-nang-khieu\/#Gia_su_Ve\" >Gia s\u01b0 V\u1ebd<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-5'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-nang-khieu\/#Gia_su_Dan_Piano\" >Gia s\u01b0 \u0110\u00e0n Piano<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-5'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-nang-khieu\/#Gia_su_Dan_Organ\" >Gia s\u01b0 \u0110\u00e0n Organ<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<h2><strong>1.Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh khi h\u1ecdc To\u00e1n?<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>To\u00e1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc kh\u00f3, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u em th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng h\u1ed5ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n to\u00e1n, m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c, ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fd, t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t\u2026<\/li>\n<li>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch m\u00f4n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i, kh\u00f4 khan.,,,<\/li>\n<li>Vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c em g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1ea1y To\u00e1n ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t s\u00f4 b\u1ea1n y\u00eau th\u00edch m\u00f4n To\u00e1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc n\u00e0y<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>=&gt;&gt;&gt; Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc To\u00e1n, c\u00e1c em g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00f3, qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay \u0111\u1ebfn\u00a0<strong>trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00ecm\u00a0<strong>gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y chuy\u00ean to\u00e1n<\/strong>\u00a0ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u00a0mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/p>\n<h2><span id=\"2_Trung_tam_gia_su_Tri_Viet_%E2%80%93_dia_chi_uy_tin_so_1_Ha_Noi\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>2.Trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh \u2013 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 uy t\u00edn s\u1ed1 1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00f9ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u trung t\u00e2m kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng\u00a0<strong>trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh Minh<\/strong>\u00a0lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh.Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i:<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1063 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su%CC%9B-ha%CC%80-no%CC%A3%CC%82i-1-e1538708745894.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"228\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 7 n\u0103m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c gia s\u01b0<\/li>\n<li>C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169\u00a0<strong>gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc danh ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/li>\n<li>H\u00e0ng n\u0103m, trung t\u00e2m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ecd, cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 cho h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc sinh<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t<\/li>\n<li>L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n kh\u00e1c<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/li>\n<li>Trung t\u00e2m cam k\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng thu b\u1ea5t c\u00fa m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0o khi t\u00ecm\u00a0<strong>gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span id=\"3_Bang_gia_gia_su_chuyen_Toan\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>3.B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n<\/strong><\/h2>\n<table width=\"641\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"641\">H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af CHUY\u00caN TO\u00c1N<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"214\">\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/td>\n<td width=\"214\">H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td>\n<td width=\"214\">Sinh vi\u00ean<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"214\">1 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/td>\n<td width=\"214\">120.000 \u2013 180.000<\/td>\n<td width=\"214\">200.000 \u2013 250.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"214\">2 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/td>\n<td width=\"214\">150.000 \u2013 250.000<\/td>\n<td width=\"214\">250.000 \u2013 300.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"214\">&gt;= 3 h\u1ecdc sinh<\/td>\n<td width=\"214\">Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn<\/td>\n<td width=\"214\">Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t tham kh\u1ea3o. H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc xin li\u00ean h\u1ec7\u00a00962.700.594\u00a0ho\u1eb7c\u00a00462.943.631\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1\u00a0<strong>gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/strong>\u00a0chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n<\/p>\n<p><em><strong>*******************************************<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><strong>=&gt;&gt;&gt;. Xem th\u00eam:\u00a0B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0\u00a0t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ef1c k\u00ec \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecf l\u1ee1<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><strong>=&gt;&gt;&gt;\u00a0 Nhanh tay \u0111\u0103ng k\u00ed t\u00ecm\u00a0gia s\u01b0 L\u00fd 12, c\u00f3 ngay sau 2 bu\u1ed5i. Cam k\u1ebft gia s\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00fang chu\u1ea9n 100% y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><strong>********************************************<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span id=\"4_Doi_ngu_gia_su_chuyen_Toan\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>4.\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n<\/strong><\/h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/giasusupham.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/gia-su-chuyen-toan-day-kem-mon-toan-lop-6.jpg\" alt=\"K\u00e1\u00ba\u00bft qu\u00e1\u00ba\u00a3 h\u00c3\u00acnh \u00e1\u00ba\u00a3nh cho gia s\u00c6\u00b0 chuy\u00c3\u00aan to\u00c3\u00a1n\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Gia\u00a0 s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/strong>\u00a0l\u00e0 c\u00e1c gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean \u0111ang gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y m\u00f4n To\u00e1n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng THCS,THPT tr\u00ean \u0111ia b\u00e0n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>L\u00e0 c\u00e1c sinh vi\u00ean s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m To\u00e1n n\u0103m 3,4 c\u1ee7a \u0110H s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/li>\n<li>Ngo\u00e0i ra, gia s\u01b0 sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f2n bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110H top \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 \u0110H B\u00e1ch Khoa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0110H Kinh t\u1ebf qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n, \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng,\u2026<\/li>\n<li>Gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 n\u0103m kinh nhi\u1ec7m trong gia s\u01b0 To\u00e1n<\/li>\n<li>Gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y linh ho\u1ea1t, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc sinh<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><center>\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-shortcode\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;3278&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;shortcode&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;8&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 post&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;5\\\/5 - (8 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Gia s\u01b0 \u0110\u00e0n Organ&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;138&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"3\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"4\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n      